The paper discusses security challenges in wireless sensor networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper also discusses the communication and processing aspects of wireless sensor networks, which are relevant to the categories of networking and distributed computing (cs.NI and cs.DC). The paper also discusses the challenges faced in implementing security mechanisms in wireless sensor networks, which is relevant to the categories of software engineering and systems (cs.SE and cs.SY).
